[13/12/2019 08:19:19] <font color="#00ff00">(R E)</font>
[13/12/2019 08:19:21] <font color="#ffffff">Sí, es bastante duro,</font>
[13/12/2019 08:19:23] <font color="#ffffff">pero te acostumbras</font>
